          <p> "Responsive design" redirects here. For the computer-aided design approach, see responsive computer-aided design.
               Not to be confused with Responsiveness.
          </p>




      <ul>
          <li>Responsive web design (RWD) is an approach to web design that makes web pages render well on a variety of devices and window or screen sizes. </li>
          <li>Recent work also considers the viewer proximity as part of the viewing context as an extension for RWD.</li>
          <li>Content, design and performance are necessary across all devices to ensure usability and satisfaction.</li>
      </ul>

